manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "timothe-rs"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "timothe-rs"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "*"
bytes = "*"
chrono = "*"
chrono-tz = "0.6.3"
dirs = "4.0.0"
futures = "*"
futures-util = "0.3.24"
log = "*"
poise = "0.3.0"
pretty_env_logger = "*"
reqwest = "*"
saffron = "0.1.0"
shellexpand = "2.1.2"

[dependencies.config]
version = "*"
features = ["toml"]

[dependencies.ical]
version = "0.7.*"
features = ["ical", "vcard"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.postcard]
version = "1.0.0"
features = ["alloc"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "*"
features = ["rc"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "*"
features = ["full"]
